(101, 1, '2016-03-28 11:25:00', '2016-03-28 11:25:00', 'If you will look at the South America map, the Andes mountain range will probably catch your eye at once. And the proud country to live besides them, ashore the Pacific Ocean is Chile. And boy, do they make a great wine! 098\r\n\r\n<!--more-->', 'Tasting Chilled Chilean Wine', 'If you will look at the South America map, the Andes mountain range will probably catch your eye at once. And the proud country to live besides them, ashore the Pacific Ocean is Chile. And boy, do they make a great wine! 123', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '11-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-03-28 11:25:00', '2016-03-28 11:25:00', '', 11, 'your_website_url_here/11-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
